elbased sweetpacks aka sweetim for approximately  million sweetpacks produced a variety of downloadable content for everyday use in january  they acquired conduit’s clientconnect business in an allstock transaction valued at  million in june  perion acquired san francisco based growmobile in february  perion acquired parisbased makemereach  a social media advertising platform after their move to holon perion network incorporated csr policies into their corporate strategy  of its net profits is donated and all employees are permitted to spend up to  hours per year volunteering in the community in december  perion acquired the digital advertising company undertone for  million in january  perion announced the appointment of new ceo doron gerstel effective april  followed by the announcement of josef mandelbaum stepping down from the company later in the year the companys unit makemereach was named as a snapchat partner productsedit undertone helps brands engage consumers through crossscreen and digital ad experiences codefuel allows developers to generate revenue using search syndication makemereach is a social media marketing tool to help advertisers grow demand for their brand on facebook twitter instagram  snapchat the mobile and desktop apps are incredimail an email program and smilebox a desktop and mobile app for customizing and animating photos see alsoedit conduit company conduit toolbar download valley referencesedit  yacov kaufman steps down as cfo of perion seasoned financial executive ophir yakovian to join perion as its cf retrieved    perion appoints mike glover former president of infospace as general manager of search business unit retrieved    perion moves closer to mobile ad tech with new acquisition the times of israel retrieved    perion network ltd new york times  a b perion to participate in adtech san francisco  new york times retrieved may    incredimail  israels incredible story wwwjpostcom retrieved    tase site  company perion network  summa