 to navigation search perion network ltd type public traded as nasdaq peri tase peri industry adtech internet founder yaron adler ofer adler headquarters holon israel area served worldwide key people doron gerstel ceo ophir yakovian cfo mike glover gm products codefuel undertone makemereach smilebox incredimail revenue us million  operating income us million  net income us million  number of employees  as of april   website perioncom perion is an israelbased adtech company providing engagement and monetization solutions for web and mobile based digital businesses their headquarters are in holon israel with offices in san francisco new york city boston chicago washington dc los angeles atlanta milan hamburg düsseldorf paris and barcelona contents  history  products  see also  references historyedit perion was formerly incredimail an email company founded in  by cousins yaron and ofer adler soon after its founding they raised  million from private and institutional sources and ipoed on nasdaq in january  they listed on the tel aviv stock exchange in  perion was managed by its original founders until august  when josef mandelbaum was appointed ceo mandelbaum had previously been ceo of american greetings interactive the internet branch of american greetings in august  perion acquired the redmondbased smilebox for  million smilebox is an application for creating slideshows and other digital photo albums in november  they changed the company name to perion the hebrew word for productivity in november  perion purchased israelbased sweetpacks aka sweetim for approximately  million sweetpacks produced a variety of downloadable content for everyday use in january  they acquired conduit’s clientconnect business in an allstock transaction valued at  million in june  perion acquired san francisco based growmobile in february  perion acquired parisbased makemereach  a social media advertising platform after their move to holon perion network incorporated csr policies into their corporate strategy  of its net profits is donated and all employees are permitted to spend up to  hours per year volunteering in the community in december  perion acquired the digital advertising company undertone for  million in january  perion announced the appointment of new ceo doron gerstel effective april  followed by the announcement of josef mandelbaum stepping down from the company later in the year the companys unit makemereach was named as a snapchat partner productsedit undertone helps brands engage consumers through crossscreen and digital ad experiences codefuel allows developers to generate revenue using search syndication makemereach is a social media marketing tool to help advertisers grow demand for their brand on facebook twitter instagram  snapchat the mobile and desktop apps are incredimail an email program and smilebox a desktop and mobile app for customizing and animating photos see alsoedit conduit company conduit toolbar download valley referencesedit  yacov kaufman steps down as cfo of perion seasoned financial executive ophir yakovian to join perion as its cf retrieved    perion appoints mike glover former president of infospace as general manager of search business unit retrieved    perion moves closer to mobile ad tech with new acquisition the times of israel retrieved    perion network ltd new york times  a b perion to participate in adtech san francisco  new york times retrieved may    incredimail  israels incredible story wwwjpostcom retrieved    tase site  company perion network  summary  share perion network    josef mandelbaum joins incredimail as chief executive officer  business wire retrieved july    smilebox to be acquired by incredimail for up to  million  aislyn greene puget sound business journal retrieved august    incredimail buys online photo album and slideshow creator smilebox for up to  million  robin wauters tech crunch retrieved august    sweetpacks acquisition call nasdaq retrieved november    holy emoticons batman —