rtone helps brands engage consumers through crossscreen and digital ad experiences codefuel allows developers to generate revenue using search syndication makemereach is a social media marketing tool to help advertisers grow demand for their brand on facebook twitter instagram  snapchat the mobile and desktop apps are incredimail an email program and smilebox a desktop and mobile app for customizing and animating photos see alsoedit conduit company conduit toolbar download valley referencesedit  yacov kaufman steps down as cfo of perion seasoned financial executive ophir yakovian to join perion as its cf retrieved    perion appoints mike glover former president of infospace as general manager of search business unit retrieved    perion moves closer to mobile ad tech with new acquisition the times of israel retrieved    perion network ltd new york times  a b perion to participate in adtech san francisco  new york times retrieved may    incredimail  israels incredible story wwwjpostcom retrieved    tase site  company perion network  summary  share perion network    josef mandelbaum joins incredimail as chief executive officer  business wire retrieved july    smilebox to be acquired by incredimail for up to  million  aislyn greene puget sound business journal retrieved august    incredimail buys online photo album and slideshow creator smilebox for up to  million  robin wauters tech crunch retrieved august    sweetpacks acquisition call nasdaq retrieved november    holy emoticons batman — perion network acquires sweetpacks for m  mike butcher tech crunch retrieved november    editorial reuters israels perion buys mobile advertising firm grow mobile reuters uk retrieved    perion extends microsoft deal ups mobile business david shamah times of israel retrieved august    perion moves closer to mobile ad tech with new acquisition david shamah times of israel retrieved february    perion in cr push following merger ethical performance  ad tech firm perion buys undertone fo