 nasdaq in january  they listed on the tel aviv stock exchange in  perion was managed by its original founders until august  when josef mandelbaum was appointed ceo mandelbaum had previously been ceo of american greetings interactive the internet branch of american greetings in august  perion acquired the redmondbased smilebox for  million smilebox is an application for creating slideshows and other digital photo albums in november  they changed the company name to perion the hebrew word for productivity in november  perion purchased israelbased sweetpacks aka sweetim for approximately  million sweetpacks produced a variety of downloadable content for everyday use in january  they acquired conduit’s clientconnect business in an allstock transaction valued at  million in june  perion acquired san francisco based growmobile in february  perion acquired parisbased makemereach  a social media advertising platform after their move to holon perion network incorporated csr policies into their corporate strategy  of its net profits is donated and all employees are permitted to spend up to  hours per year volunteering in the community in december  perion acquired the digital advertising company undertone for  million in january  perion announced the appointment of new ceo doron gerstel effective april  followed by the announcement of josef mandelbaum stepping down from the company later in the year the companys unit makemereach was named as a snapchat partner productsedit undertone helps brands engage consumers through crossscreen and digital ad experiences codefuel allows developers to generate revenue using search syndication makemereach is a social media marketing tool to help advertisers grow demand for their brand on facebook twitter instagram  snapchat the mobile and desktop apps are incredimail an email program and smilebox a desktop and mobile app for customizing and animating photos see alsoedit conduit company conduit toolbar download valley referencesedit  yacov k